01:32:20,960 --> 01:32:22,400
[SPEAKER_01] Pa mi još nismo.

685
01:32:22,720 --> 01:32:23,440
[SPEAKER_03] Pa mi još nismo.

686
01:32:23,680 --> 01:32:25,840
